snippet.title: NATIVES
snippet.description:
Natives makes use of Google Street View Panoramas to hack real people in places. It's not realistic, it's REAL. Download on Google Play Store to believe. ~Violet

Download now! https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.loyalsheep.Natives

~~Features~~

• First of its kind.
• Makes use of Google Street View Panoramas.
• Intelligent touch controls and gestures.
• Consists of nearly all the major cities of the world. 
• Seamless loading between the levels.
• Awesome soundtracks.
• A great story, perhaps?
• Most 'informal' game on Play Store.
• Made by one person, that's not a feature but yeah!
• It's free without any ads.

Visit us at: http://loyalsheep.com for more information.

Song: Glude - Identity [NCS Release]
Music provided by NoCopyrightSounds.
Video Link: https://youtu.be/_z1mdKOw6PQ
Download Link: http://NCS.lnk.to/Identity
